sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant R as React Frontend
    participant E as Express API
    participant A as Auth Middleware
    participant C as Controller / Route
    participant S as Service
    participant M as Mongoose Model
    participant DB as MongoDB

    U->>R: Fills form / clicks button
    R->>E: HTTP request + JWT in Authorization header
    E->>A: requireAuth(req, res, next)
    A->>A: Verify JWT + load user
    A->>C: next() with req.user
    C->>S: Call service (e.g. flashcardGenerator)
    S->>M: Query / create / update
    M->>DB: Mongoose executes BSON operation
    DB-->>M: Document(s)
    M-->>S: Plain object(s)
    S-->>C: Result
    C-->>E: res.json(result)
    E-->>R: JSON response
    R-->>U: Updated UI
